resources.string: Ibhethri lakho lisemjikelezweni wokushaja wama-375. Ngenxa yokuthi kungase kube nenkinga yokushisha ngokweqile kwebhethri, lapho ibhethri yakho ifinyelela umjikelezo wokushaja wama-400 womthambo webhethri futhi isivinini sokushaja sizoncipha futhi kunconywa ukuba kushintshwe ibhethri. Okungakhethwa kosekelo kuyatholakala, vakashela okuthi <u>g.co/pixel/6abattery</u> ukuze uthole ulwazi olwengeziwe.

Ngenxa yokuthi kungenzeka kube nenkinga yokushisa ngokweqile kwebhethri, umthamo webhethri kanye nesivinini sokushaja kuncishisiwe, futhi kunconywa ukuba kushintshwe ibhethri. Okungakhethwa kosekelo kuyatholakala, vakashela okuthi <u>g.co/pixel/6abattery</u> ukuze uthole ulwazi olwengeziwe.
